title: Persistence Pays Off For Aztecs' DB
text:
Persistence Pays Off For Aztecs' DB - KMPH FOX 26 | Central San Joaquin Valley News Source Member Center: Persistence Pays Off For Aztecs' DB Posted: rwood@kmph.com 
San Diego State senior cornerback J.J. Whittaker is one of the top defensive backs in the Mountain West Conference. 
Whittaker has been around awhile. This is his sixth year with the Aztecs. He lost his first three seasons to various injuries and was granted the extra year on a medical hardship. Now he has developed into a star player and a team leader. His teammates say Whittaker's dedication and persistence have inspired and motivated them. 
San Diego State will host Fresno State Saturday night. The Bulldogs are 1-3 with a three game losing streak.
